versions.name: DragBuildPowerTower
versions.description: This mod allows you to drag build multiple wireless power towers. They can be built diagonally, no need to align with latitude or longitude lines. 这个mod允许你拖动建造输电塔，并且可以斜着造，而不需要对齐经纬线。

versions.name: RecycleableFuelRods
versions.description: After the generators burning the deuteron fuel rods or the antimatter fuel rods, you will get the empty rods back. You can use that to make new full rods by only adding fuels in empty rods. 发电厂烧完燃料棒会返还空的燃料棒，你可以往里面加燃料生产新的燃料棒。
